J. Bergmann, "Gebet and Zauberspruch," *MGWJ*, LXXIV (1930), 457-463; H.
G. Endow, "Kawwana: The Struggle for Inwardness in Judaism," Studies in
Jewish Literature in Honor of Prof. Kaufmann Kohler (Berlin 1913),
